description: Will buy used cell phones & electronics
overview:
Cellitused.com, Inc. was launched in late 2005. Cellitused was one of the few pioneers of the cell phone buy-back revolution and now has grown into one of the top buyers of new, used, and broken cell phones, iPhones, iPods, iPads, and other small electronic devices.

Cellitused offers the best prices for hundreds of devices and has kept over 35,000 devices from reaching our landfills. Cellitused has been mentioned in The New York Times, Chicago Tribune, ABC News and MarketWatch.
